'''路易丝·穆希基瓦博'''（{{lang-rw|Louise Mushikiwabo}}，{{bd|1961年|5月22日||}}），现任[[法语国家及地区国际组织|法语国家及地区国际组织]]秘书长。曾于2009年到2018年任{{tsl|en|Ministry of Foreign Affairs and Cooperation (Rwanda)|卢旺达外交与合作部|卢旺达外交部长}}，以及新闻部长兼任政府发言人。

2018年10月12日，在[[亚美尼亚|亚美尼亚]]首都[[叶里温|叶里温]]举行的法语国家峰会上获选为组织秘书长。

== 早年 ==
路易丝·穆希基瓦博于1961年5月22日在[[卢旺达|卢旺达]]首都[[吉佳利|吉佳利]]出生<ref name="Twagilimana">{{cite book |last=Twagilimana |first=Aimable |title=Historical Dictionary of Rwanda |date=2015-11-06 |isbn=9781442255913 |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=9E6xCgAAQBAJ&pg=PA157 |access-date=2021-04-08 |archive-date=2021-08-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210818211429/https://books.google.com/books?id=9E6xCgAAQBAJ&pg=PA157 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，父亲是图西人，在殖民者的咖啡种植园当[[簿记|簿记]]，兼经营家里的小公司{{sfn|Mushikiwabo|Kramer|2007|p=65}}。母亲是哲学历史学家{{tsl|en|Alexis Kagame|亚历克西斯·卡加梅}}的表姐{{sfn|Mushikiwabo|Kramer|2007|p=Dedications}}。路易丝在吉佳利度过童年<ref name="Nkem-Eneanya">{{cite web |last=Nkem-Eneanya |first=Jennifer |date=2013-11-27 |title=Minister Louise Mushikiwabo; Rebuilding Rwanda One Policy at a Time… |website=Konnect Africa |url=http://www.konnectafrica.net/minister-louise-mushikiwabo-rebuilding-rwanda-one-policy-at-a-time/ |access-date=2021-04-08 |archive-date=2021-01-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210118204826/https://www.konnectafrica.net/minister-louise-mushikiwabo-rebuilding-rwanda-one-policy-at-a-time/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。她是九个兄弟姐妹中最小的一个<ref name="NewTimes2008">{{cite news |newspaper=The New Times |location=Rwanda |date=2008-03-08 |title=New faces in Cabinet |url=http://www.newtimes.co.rw/section/article/2008-03-08/86852/ |accessdate=2021-04-08 |archive-date=2017-02-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170202025705/http://www.newtimes.co.rw/section/article/2008-03-08/86852/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，哥哥{{tsl|en|Lando Ndasingwa|兰多·恩达辛瓦}}是卢旺达知名商人兼政治人物，曾于[[朱韦纳尔·哈比亚利马纳|朱韦纳尔·哈比亚利马纳]]政府担任劳工和社会事务部长，1994年[[卢旺达种族灭绝|卢旺达种族灭绝]]中遇害<ref>[http://www.crimesofwar.org/tribun-mag/mag_rwandatestim.html Mushikiwabo's Autobiography on the site crimesofwar.org] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20041205003622/http://www.crimesofwar.org/tribun-mag/mag_rwandatestim.html |date=2004-12-05 }}</ref>。姐姐{{tsl|en|Anne-Marie Kantengwa|安娜-玛丽·坎滕瓦}}继承了{{tsl|en|Chez Lando|兰多酒店}}，2003年和2008年出任[[卢旺达议会|卢旺达议会]]议员<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ieew.org/2013-ptb-students/anne-marie-kantengwa |title=Anne-Marie Kantengwa |publisher=The Institute for Economic Empowerment of Women |access-date=2016-10-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170202000717/http://www.ieew.org/2013-ptb-students/anne-marie-kantengwa |archive-date=2017-02-02 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

在吉佳利上完小学和中学，穆希基瓦博于1981年到南方城市[[布塔雷|布塔雷]]的{{tsl|en|National University of Rwanda|卢旺达国立大学}}（现[[卢旺达大学|卢旺达大学]]）深造<ref name="Twagilimana"/>，1984年凭英语学士学位毕业，在中学任教过一段时间<ref name="Twagilimana"/>。1986年移民美国<ref>{{cite magazine |url=http://www.duchessinternationalmagazine.com/profile/louise-mushikiwabo/ |title=Louise Mushikiwabo |magazine=Duchess International Magazine |date=2016-01-08 |access-date=2016-10-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170908032105/http://www.duchessinternationalmagazine.com/profile/louise-mushikiwabo/ |archive-date=2017-09-08 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，到[[特拉华大学|特拉华大学]]攻读法语语言及口译硕士学位<ref name="UniversityOfDelaware">{{cite web |url=http://www1.udel.edu/udaily/2015/oct/rwanda-minister-101414.html |last=Adams |first=Elizabeth |title=Rwanda overcomes tragedy |publisher=University of Delaware |date=2014-10-14 |access-date=2016-10-19 |archive-date=2018-10-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181011172858/http://www1.udel.edu/udaily/2015/oct/rwanda-minister-101414.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。1988年完成学业留在美国，定居[[华盛顿哥伦比亚特区|华盛顿哥伦比亚特区]]<ref name="CrisafulliRedmond">{{cite book |year=2012 |last1=Crisafulli |first1=Patricia |last2=Redmond |first2=Andrea |title=Rwanda, Inc.: How a Devastated Nation Became an Economic Model for the Developing World |publisher=Macmillan |isbn=9781137066473 |page=30 |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=wilyjMI3UxcC&pg=PT30}}</ref>。之后供职游说组织，后来赴突尼斯，任职[[非洲开发银行|非洲开发银行]]<ref name="CrisafulliRedmond"/>，官至通讯主任<ref name="NewTimes2008"/>。

2006年与美国记者、前[[美国海军陆战队|海军陆战队员]]杰克·克莱默（Jack Karmer）<ref>{{cite web |author=Macmillan Publishers |title=Jack Kramer |url=https://us.macmillan.com/author/jackkramer/ |access-date=2017-11-16 |archive-date=2020-08-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200813123127/https://us.macmillan.com/author/jackkramer |dead-url=no }}</ref>撰写著作《卢旺达是世界的》（''Rwanda Means the Universe''）<ref name="Waters">{{cite journal |last=Waters |first=Tony |title=Rwanda Means the Universe: A Native's Memoir of Blood and Bloodlines |journal=The International Journal of African Historical Studies |url=https://www.questia.com/library/journal/1P3-1243349371/rwanda-means-the-universe-a-native-s-memoir-of-blood |access-date=2017-11-16 |archive-date=2019-07-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190716110903/https://www.questia.com/library/journal/1P3-1243349371/rwanda-means-the-universe-a-native-s-memoir-of-blood |dead-url=no }}</ref>。这部半自传式的著作讲述了穆希基瓦博家族的历史、她在卢旺达的早年及移民到美国的生活<ref name="Waters"/>，也从历史及穆希基瓦博个人的观点迅速[[卢旺达种族灭绝|卢旺达种族灭绝]]，当中提到她在华盛顿生活时听到许多家人遇害的消息<ref name="Waters"/>。

== 政治生涯 ==
2008年3月，穆希基瓦博受卢旺达总统[[保罗·卡加梅|保罗·卡加梅]]邀请回国，接任洛朗·恩库西（Laurent Nkusi）<ref>{{cite news |last=Munyaneza |first=James |title=Umuco saga: Why all eyes are on new Minister Mushikiwabo |newspaper=The New Times |date=2008-03-26 |url=http://www.newtimes.co.rw/section/article/2008-03-26/3130/ |access-date=2016-10-19 |archive-date=2017-02-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170202025525/http://www.newtimes.co.rw/section/article/2008-03-26/3130/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>出任信息部长一职<ref name="NewTimes2008"/>。任期早年负责决定是否向诽谤卡加梅的几家地方媒体采取行动<ref name="GovernmentPrintingOffice">{{cite book|title=Country Reports on Human Rights Practices 2009|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=7NMXABwIjyAC&pg=PA528|publisher=Government Printing Office|pages=528–|id=GGKEY:EXCA0EGBR49|access-date=2021-04-08|archive-date=2017-10-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171010044143/https://books.google.com/books?id=7NMXABwIjyAC&pg=PA528|dead-url=no}}</ref>，其中卢旺达语日报《Umuco》曾将卡加梅比作[[阿道夫·希特勒|阿道夫·希特勒]]，媒体高等理事会故要求政府扣押该报的执照<ref>{{cite news |last=Munyaneza |first=James |title=Suspend Umuco, HCP tells new Information Minister |newspaper=The New Times |date=2008-03-24 |url=http://www.newtimes.co.rw/section/article/2008-03-24/3119/ |access-date=2016-10-19 |archive-date=2017-02-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170202025548/http://www.newtimes.co.rw/section/article/2008-03-24/3119/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。恩库西驳回该请求，穆希基瓦博也未采取行动，但该报仍于2008年10月停刊<ref name="GovernmentPrintingOffice"/>。穆希基瓦博经常鼓励同事尊重[[新闻自由|新闻自由]]<ref>{{cite news |last=Musoni |first=Edwin |title=Media has a right to public information–Mushikiwabo |newspaper=The New Times |date=2008-05-03 |url=http://www.newtimes.co.rw/section/article/2008-05-03/40028/ |access-date=2016-10-19 |archive-date=2017-02-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170202031127/http://www.newtimes.co.rw/section/article/2008-05-03/40028/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但也确保媒体遵守有关{{tsl|en|genocide denial|种族灭绝否定论}}的严苛法律<ref>{{cite news |last=Nkurunziza |first=Sam |title=Mushikiwabo warns media on Genocide reporting |newspaper=The New Times |date=2009-04-27 |url=http://www.newtimes.co.rw/section/article/2009-04-27/8220/ |access-date=2016-10-19 |archive-date=2017-02-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170202030003/http://www.newtimes.co.rw/section/article/2009-04-27/8220/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2009年，她暂时禁止卢旺达语电台转播[[英国广播公司|英国广播公司]]的节目，认为BBC播出的节目“为种族灭绝主义者和种族灭绝否定论者提供自由空间”<ref name="BBC2009">{{cite news |publisher=BBC News |title=Rwanda bans BBC local broadcasts |date=2009-04-26 |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/world/africa/8019398.stm |access-date=2016-10-19 |archive-date=2009-04-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090429223227/http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/world/africa/8019398.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。BBC对此表示否认，认为公司和卢旺达政府对种族灭绝的表述各有不同<ref name="BBC2009"/>。

除了负责部门决策，穆希基瓦博还充当政府发言人<ref name="MediaMissMushikiwabo">{{cite news |last=Munyaneza |first=James |date=2009-12-08 |title=Why the media will miss Mushikiwabo |url=http://www.newtimes.co.rw/section/read/14354 |access-date=2017-11-17 |archive-date=2020-08-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200803175413/https://www.newtimes.co.rw/section/read/14354 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。卡加梅总统的首席礼宾官{{tsl|en|Rose Kabuye|罗斯·卡布耶}}在德国被捕，引发两国之间的外交危机，期间穆希基瓦博作为代表，向国际媒体阐释卢旺达政府的立场<ref name="RwandaCongoKabuye">{{cite news |last=McGreal |first=Chris |date=2008-11-10 |title=Top Rwandan aide chooses French terror trial |newspaper=The Guardian |url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/2008/nov/10/rwanda-congo-kabuye |accessdate=2021-04-08 |archive-date=2021-02-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210227002302/http://www.theguardian.com/world/2008/nov/10/rwanda-congo-kabuye |dead-url=no }}</ref>。她利用个人语言特长，用卢旺达语、法语和英语发表声明<ref name="MediaMissMushikiwabo"/>。

